{"TopicId":177402,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Which mod adds the the info box near the NavBall.","CreatedByName":"BlackHat","CreatedById":138278,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-08T03:11:17Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"BlackHat","CreatedById":138278,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-08T03:11:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have had this little info box, that for a long time I thought was a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Engineer Redux (mod)\u0022\u003EKER\u003C/abbr\u003E info box\u00A0(Like their Hud1 \u0026amp; Hud2)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think I figured out which mod it was way back when I was playing in 1.0.5. But that was LONG ago and I have no idea which mod it is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMainly I wanted to know so I could move it to the side, when\u00A0I am launching rockets that the\u00A0exhaust is not directly behind it making it un-readable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Which_Mod.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022540\u0022 src=\u0022https://image.ibb.co/mVZSmK/Which_Mod.jpg\u0022 width=\u0022960\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-08-08T03:11:54Z\u0022 title=\u002208/08/2018 03:11  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 8, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by BlackHat\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-08T03:20:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s Navhud. It also added all those lines.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not sure how configurable that info is. I\u0027ve never changed it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BlackHat","CreatedById":138278,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-08T05:41:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks. Yep NavHud is a favorite...\u00A0 I will have to see if there is something to adjust that box in the mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BlackHat","CreatedById":138278,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-08T06:27:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223429862\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022177402\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221533698456\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s Navhud. It also added all those lines.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not sure how configurable that info is. I\u0027ve never changed it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFound it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe mod creates a config file when the game is run.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGameData\\NavHud\\Plugins\\PluginData\\NavHud\\config.xml\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nin it there is a section for the text block.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E    \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;rect\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atn\u0022\u003Ename\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atv\u0022\u003E\u0022hud text position\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n        \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;xmin\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E940\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;/xmin\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n        \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;xmax\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E1145\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;/xmax\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n        \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;ymin\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E756\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;/ymin\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n        \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;ymax\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E876\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;/ymax\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n    \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;/rect\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just reduced the x values by 200 to shift it to the left. Works great.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0026lt;xmin\u0026gt;740\u0026lt;/xmin\u0026gt;\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u0026lt;xmax\u0026gt;945\u0026lt;/xmax\u0026gt;\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022NavHud.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://image.ibb.co/e6KibK/NavHud.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-11T16:47:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUmmm....not to put a damper on your \u0022solution\u0022 but;\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is a simple checkbox in the NavHud GUI that unlocks that text block so you can move it around.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe color can be changed as well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00224DA475DE11777CE90A062913FE2FB34714C674CC\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/955213082866364658/4DA475DE11777CE90A062913FE2FB34714C674CC/\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Lock HUD Text\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSometimes we jump to looking for zebras when we haven\u0027t even checked for horses.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-08-11T16:59:38Z\u0022 title=\u002208/11/2018 04:59  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 11, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Rocket In My Pocket\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BlackHat","CreatedById":138278,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-11T20:34:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAhh, I long ago\u00A0\u0022hid\u0022 my NavHud toolbar button, (Since I never turn it off) and forgot about it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}